-1 INSTRUCTION10~
  Socials:
    These are commands such as "GRIN" or "LAUGH" that in general do not change
the play of the game.  They do convey a physical or emotional aspect to most
conversations with other players. Without these commands, most conversation will
appear dry, or have that "missing something" feel.  Socials are not found in the
HELP system, and must be tried individually.  There is a command that lists all
of the social commands.  Socials may be done at someone, ex. "GRIN BILBO".

