-1 INSTRUCTION11~
			    The Character:

  The character has several primary components:
    1)  Personalization.        (Character name and title)
    2)  Background of study.    (Character class and race)
    3)  Statistics.             (Character attributes)
    4)  Languages.
    5)  Equipment.

  Each of these components should be understood and decided upon before
character generation should continue.  At any time, the character may quit his
character, until reaching 2nd level, and not expect the character to save.  This
also means that the player must be prepared to reach at least second level
immediately after character generation.

