-1 RSETEXTRA~
  This allows you to attach extra descriptions to a room in your castle.  Extra
descriptions allow a person to type "look <keyword>" and see the description
that you typed in.  Each description has a keyword and an associated
description.  You can also DELete unwanted extra descriptions (see NOTE).
To create a keyword list for a description, you would use this format:
  >rset extra keyword <keyword_list>
Then, you would attach a description to those keywords by useing this format:
  >rset extra desc <keyword> <description>
